Author: not_the_cicada
Text: Ugh, me too. Felt too weak to even lift up a pencil. Laid in bed all day (also had my period). I ended up having a can of tuna in a big salad with tons of veggies, and also made myself a small Huel shake.   If you can, try to add some nutrients in - I’m feeling SO much better today after just the kind of “meh” effort I made yesterday. I hope you feel better! 💕

Author: moonchldx
Text: I can relate... was so fatigued yesterday I laid in bed all day and could barley walk. No fun no fun at all
